headline: 4 Chemical Stocks Poised to Outshine Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: DuPont (DD), Eastman Chemical (EMN), Avient (AVNT) and Albemarle (ALB) are likely to have benefited from cost and productivity actions amid soft demand in Q4.
